      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Advances in Computer Games 17</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_16\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 16\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_18&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 18 (page does not exist)\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p><p><b>Advances in Computer Games 17</b>,<br />\nNovember 23-25, <a href=\"/Timeline#2021\" title=\"Timeline\">2021</a>, held online. ACG is the conference of the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Keynote_Speakers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Keynote Speakers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Accepted_Papers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Accepted Papers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Keynote_Speakers\">Keynote Speakers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_17&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Keynote Speakers\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/David_Silver\" title=\"David Silver\">David Silver</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Michael_Bowling\" title=\"Michael Bowling\">Michael Bowling</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Lefler\" title=\"Mark Lefler\">Mark Lefler</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Larry_Kaufman\" title=\"Larry Kaufman\">Larry Kaufman</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Accepted_Papers\">Accepted Papers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_17&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Accepted Papers\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicolas_Fabiano&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nicolas Fabiano (page does not exist)\">Nicolas Fabiano</a>, <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Sequential Halving Using Scores</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>  (<b>2021</b>). <i>Solving Bicoloring-Graph Games on Rectangular Boards — Part 1: Partisan Col and Snort</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a>  (<b>2021</b>). <i>Solving Bicoloring-Graph Games on Rectangular Boards — Part 2: Impartial Col and Snort</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Cheng_Yueh&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Cheng Yueh (page does not exist)\">Cheng Yueh</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gang-Yu_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gang-Yu Fan (page does not exist)\">Gang-Yu Fan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ting-Yu_Lin&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ting-Yu Lin (page does not exist)\">Ting-Yu Lin</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Opponent Model Selection Using Deep Learning</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Julien_Sentuc&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Julien Sentuc (page does not exist)\">Julien Sentuc</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mathurin_Videau&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mathurin Videau (page does not exist)\">Mathurin Videau</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Cosine Annealing, Mixnet and Swish Activation for Computer Go</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gilad_Moskowitz&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gilad Moskowitz (page does not exist)\">Gilad Moskowitz</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Vadim_Ponomarenko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vadim Ponomarenko (page does not exist)\">Vadim Ponomarenko</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>A Heuristic Approach to the Game of Sylver Coinage</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryan_Hayward\" title=\"Ryan Hayward\">Ryan Hayward</a>, et al. (<b>2021</b>). <i>BoxOff is NP-complete</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Rejwana_Haque&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Rejwana Haque (page does not exist)\">Rejwana Haque</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ting_Han_Wei&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ting Han Wei (page does not exist)\">Ting Han Wei</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>On the Road to Perfection? Evaluating Leela Chess Zero Against Endgame Tablebases</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mark_Goadrich&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mark Goadrich (page does not exist)\">Mark Goadrich</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Collin_Shaddox&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Collin Shaddox (page does not exist)\">Collin Shaddox</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Quantifying the Space of Hearts Variants</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lucas_Gnecco_Heredia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lucas Gnecco Heredia (page does not exist)\">Lucas Gnecco Heredia</a>, <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Expert Iteration for Risk</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Satoshi_Tanaka&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Satoshi Tanaka (page does not exist)\">Satoshi Tanaka</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Francois_Bonnet&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Francois Bonnet (page does not exist)\">François Bonnet</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=S%C3%A9bastien_Tixeuil&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sébastien Tixeuil (page does not exist)\">Sébastien Tixeuil</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Yasumasa_Tamura&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Yasumasa Tamura (page does not exist)\">Yasumasa Tamura</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Quixo Is Solved</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Boris_Doux&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Boris Doux (page does not exist)\">Boris Doux</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Benjamin_Negrevergne&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Benjamin Negrevergne (page does not exist)\">Benjamin Negrevergne</a>, <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Deep Reinforcement Learning for Morpion Solitaire</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthew_Stephenson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Matthew Stephenson (page does not exist)\">Matthew Stephenson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Eric_Piette&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Eric Piette (page does not exist)\">Eric Piette</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Soemers&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dennis Soemers (page does not exist)\">Dennis Soemers</a>, <a href=\"/Cameron_Browne\" title=\"Cameron Browne\">Cameron Browne</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Automatic Generation of Board Game Manuals</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Cheng_Yi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Cheng Yi (page does not exist)\">Cheng Yi</a>, <a href=\"/Tomoyuki_Kaneko\" title=\"Tomoyuki Kaneko\">Tomoyuki Kaneko</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Improving Counterfactual Regret Minimization Agents Training in card game Cheat Using Ordered Abstraction</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Soemers&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dennis Soemers (page does not exist)\">Dennis Soemers</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Eric_Piette&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Eric Piette (page does not exist)\">Eric Piette</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthew_Stephenson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Matthew Stephenson (page does not exist)\">Matthew Stephenson</a>, <a href=\"/Cameron_Browne\" title=\"Cameron Browne\">Cameron Browne</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Optimised Playout Implementations for the Ludii General Game System</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Keita_Fujihira&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Keita Fujihira (page does not exist)\">Keita Fujihira</a>, <a href=\"/Chu-Hsuan_Hsueh\" title=\"Chu-Hsuan Hsueh\">Chu-Hsuan Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/Kokolo_Ikeda\" title=\"Kokolo Ikeda\">Kokolo Ikeda</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Procedural Maze Generation with Considering Difficulty from Human Players’ Perspectives</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=A%C3%B0alsteinn_P%C3%A1lsson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Aðalsteinn Pálsson (page does not exist)\">Aðalsteinn Pálsson</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Evaluating Interpretability Methods for DNNs in Game-Playing Agents</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Miha_Bizjak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Miha Bizjak (page does not exist)\">Miha Bizjak</a>, <a href=\"/Matej_Guid\" title=\"Matej Guid\">Matej Guid</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Automatic Recognition of Similar Chess Motifs</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=M._Akif_Gunes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"M. Akif Gunes (page does not exist)\">M. Akif Gunes</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=M._Fatih_Kavum&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"M. Fatih Kavum (page does not exist)\">M. Fatih Kavum</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Sanem_Sariel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sanem Sariel (page does not exist)\">Sanem Sariel</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>A Generic Approach for Player Modelling Using Event-Trait Mapping Supported by PCA</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Cameron_Browne\" title=\"Cameron Browne\">Cameron Browne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Eric_Piette&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Eric Piette (page does not exist)\">Eric Piette</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthew_Stephenson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Matthew Stephenson (page does not exist)\">Matthew Stephenson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dennis_Soemers&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dennis Soemers (page does not exist)\">Dennis Soemers</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>General Board Geometry</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Dave_Gomboc\" title=\"Dave Gomboc\">Dave Gomboc</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_R._Shelton&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian R. Shelton (page does not exist)\">Christian R. Shelton</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i>Chess endgame compression via logic minimization</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Advances in Computer Games 17</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_17&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=3328\">Advances in Computer Games 2021 | ICGA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lpcm.hypotheses.org/19162\">Conference&#160;: Advances in Computer Games 2021 (International Computer Games Association, online) | LPCM</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_17&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit sectio